---
import TechCard from "@components/experience/TechCard.astro";
---

<section
  class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full max-w-4xl m-auto max-md:flex-col max-md:mx-[0.5rem] max-md:items-start"
  id="experience"
>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      width="40"
      height="40"
      stroke-width="2"
    >
      <path
        d="M3 9a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-14a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-9z"
      ></path>
      <path d="M8 7v-2a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2"></path>
    </svg>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold">Work Experience</h2>
  </div>
  <ol class="relative">
    <li>
      <div
        class="relative mx-12 pb-12 before:absolute before:left-[-35px] before:block before:h-full before:border-l-2 before:border-white/15 before:content-[''] md:grid-cols-5 md:gap-10 md:space-x-4]"
      >
        <span class="text-jacaranda-300 -left-[44px] top-3 absolute text-5xl"
          >•</span
        >
        <time datetime="" class="text-xs font-thin">August 2025 - Current</time
        >
        <h3 class="text-jacaranda-300 font-semibold text-2xl">
          Frontend Developer
        </h3>
        <a
          href="https://www.reservi.co/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">Reservi</h4>
        </a>

        <p class="text-white/70">
         Engineer scalable, user-focused features and reusable component architectures 
leveraging React.js and modern JavaScript ecosystems. Drive application 
performance optimization and ensure cross-browser compatibility across diverse 
platforms. Lead API integrations, facilitate code reviews, and partner with cross
functional teams.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
          <TechCard>
            React.js
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            TailwindCSS
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            TypeScript
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Next.js
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Git
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Figma
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Scrum
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            RESTful APIs
          </TechCard>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div
        class="relative mx-12 pb-12 before:absolute before:left-[-35px] before:block before:h-full before:border-l-2 before:border-white/15 before:content-[''] md:grid-cols-5 md:gap-10 md:space-x-4]"
      >
        <span class="text-jacaranda-300 -left-[44px] top-3 absolute text-5xl"
          >•</span
        >
        <time datetime="" class="text-xs font-thin">January 2023 - October 2025</time
        >
        <h3 class="text-jacaranda-300 font-semibold text-2xl">
          Software Engineer
        </h3>
        <a
          href="https://www.uninorte.edu.co/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">Universidad del Norte</h4>
        </a>

        <p class="text-white/70">
          Delivered technical support for ID Uninorte and contributed to the migration and 
development of Hola Uninorte's new version. Executed multiple automation 
initiatives that streamlined internal workflows and mentored team members on 
Liferay CMS development.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
          <TechCard>
            HTML5
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            CSS3
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            JavaScript
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            PHP
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            MySQL
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            GitHub
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Figma
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Dart
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Flutter
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            CMS Liferay 7.3
          </TechCard>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div
        class="relative mx-12 pb-12 before:absolute before:left-[-35px] before:block before:h-full before:border-l-2 before:border-white/15 before:content-[''] md:grid-cols-5 md:gap-10 md:space-x-4]"
      >
        <span class="text-jacaranda-300 -left-[44px] top-3 absolute text-5xl"
          >•</span
        >
        <time datetime="" class="text-xs font-thin"
          >January 2022 - December 2022</time
        >
        <h3 class="text-jacaranda-300 font-semibold text-2xl">
          Junior Developer
        </h3>
        <a
          href="https://www.uninorte.edu.co/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">Universidad del Norte</h4>
        </a>

        <p class="text-white/70">
          I worked as a junior developer on the New Media team at the Uninorte 
Communications Office, developing components for email campaigns and creating 
functional web components to improve the user content editing experience.
        </p>
         <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
          <TechCard>
            HTML5
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            CSS3
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            JavaScript
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            Figma
          </TechCard>
          <TechCard>
            CMS Liferay 7.3
          </TechCard>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

<style>
  section span svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>
